hardn (1.1.8) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Added `detect_environment` to `hardn-setup.sh` for identifying bare metal or virtual machine environments.
  * Updated `main` in `hardn-setup.sh` to include environment detection for golden image builds.
  * Added `validate_environment` to `hardn-packages.sh` for validating system environment configurations.
  * Enhanced `validate_packages` in `hardn-packages.sh` to include environment validation.

